can we build hooks on hook level like 

└── hooks/
    ├── manifest.json            # Hook orchestration

so settings.json  look something like 

{
  "hooks": {
    "import": ".claude/hooks/manifest.json"
  },

  "projectConfig": {
    "import": ".claude/config/project.json"
  }
}

and would like to have place for easy config debug of env variables like HOOK_DIR and similar

